videos.headline: UNC RB  Williams picks up 48 yards

videos.headline: UNC's Brown scores from 12 yards out

videos.headline: East Carolina WR's one-handed catch leads to TD
videos.description: East Carolina's Darius Pinnix snags a one-handed catch near the sideline, leading to a 1-yard touchdown run by Holton Ahlers.
